response.original_title: Faraweek Finale - Memories of the Future
response.overview: Forgotten and desperate for fame, Mr Pac battles endless visions of assassin J. Wick stealing a legendary lightning bolt that rewinds time. Joined by Bart S. and a Minion, he uncovers the truth: the visions are failed loops. To break free, Mr Pac must sacrifice the past and accept the pain of moving on.
